   ╭─[ compiler-test:6:20 ]
   │
 6 │             assert(fin_foo(a) == fin_foo(a));
   │ 
   │ Help: Both operands are unit values (e.g. the return of `Mapping::set` or other side-effecting calls), so the comparison has no runtime effect. If you meant to compare values, change the operands to expressions that produce non-unit values.
